data.title: Country Abbreviations – Sustainable Sources LLC
data.text:
Can’t find the country you’re interested in here? We’ve listed all the ones we currently know – but things are always changing. Look it up on Wikipedia! Enter “http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/country” (replacing “country” with the name of the country you’re interested in). In the right sidebar you’ll usually find the “Internet TLD” (internet top level domain) for the country in question. Good luck!

Please report corrections to our list.
